<main class="contact-container">
    <div class="contact-info">
        <h1>Wellness Support</h1>
        <p>Have questions about our herbal phaki or your digestive health? We're here to guide you on your journey to natural balance. Fill out the form, and our specialists will reach out to you shortly.</p>
        
        <div class="info-item">
            <h3>Follow Our Journey</h3>
            <div class="social-links" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <a href="#" style="color: var(--primary);"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg></a>
